Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山上有個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是神山  好壯觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘  來碗蕎麥麵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  兩份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有酒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.98,0:01:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  讓我放一下  小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是  要是沒人去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算誰去了也只是重蹈覆轍而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然現在不能進山裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無直大師不是也說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這正關係到他的安全啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山裡發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是蟲師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡山的狀況有點怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得自己幫得上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  蟲師？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說他是蟲師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長老
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  請一定要幫幫我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請找找住在這深山裡的蟲師無直大師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這山裡住著全能的山神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無直大師是唯一知曉神意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做任何事的時候我們都先請示大師的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在收割的季節我們不能進入深山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是大師定下的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在無直大師突然消失後不久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.56,0:03:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幾個人打破禁忌進入深山找他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果得了熱病而丟了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精氣很重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點甜又有點苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛滲進皮膚一般的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光脈的主流
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命之河流淌的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且現在是收穫的季節
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使普通的山上精氣也會增加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒準備的話一定會中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡應該有守護光脈主流的靈獸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山的異變也許是因為靈獸的變化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  那個蟲師應該知道原因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裡的小孩嗎？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找無直大師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無直大師的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連弟子也有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個含在嘴裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭暈的時候就嚼一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是提神的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  老實待在這裡別動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始由我來找你的師父
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問「葎」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「葎」是一種宛如山的神經的蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們的意識游走於草木之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到別處看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去山的另一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊已經看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「葎」自動脫離了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐘聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在大概七點了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有鐘嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無直大師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說  是因為腳滑了而受傷囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直吃周圍的果實和草度日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水我自己有帶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有我幫忙傳達神意村裡人一定很困惑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也真是的  竟然被同為蟲師的人救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫銀古
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫無直
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄉下人不懂什麼禮節
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這大山就像我自己的庭院一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過居然在那種地方滑了腳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我真是老了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是該卸任的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指「山神」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能將我這個入侵者控制的「葎」彈開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是靈獸能辦的到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是人的法術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先前山的異變是因為你在崖邊無法動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法四處施法造成的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不過等明天我這腳好了我又能扮演「山神」了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山也會恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但據說人來做靈獸的工作很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道有什麼苦衷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有一條光脈的主流
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來有正統的靈獸來抑止山上的靈氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過被村裡的人誤殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始是河水有酒的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著草木因為過度生長而幾乎全部腐爛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也是旅行的蟲師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常會在這村子裡借宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看到這裡的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決心留下來做這裡的「山神」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻子因為長期生活在精氣迷漫的山上而過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你想讓這個孩子做下屆的「山神」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在這山上行走  他資質還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是大山撫養的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你注意到村裡小孩的數量了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝了山上流下的水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:10:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人們都會孕育很多小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,養不活的就被遺棄到山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有被野獸吃掉而活下來的只有這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是村裡這孩子的兄弟都夭折了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年前這孩子的雙親把他領回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們真是自私呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  你說得沒錯  但是也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他還是留在父母身邊比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐘聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚還有？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一直這麼輾轉流浪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我體內寄生了很多蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一個地方住下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出半年就會出現蟲的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我使用蟲的必然代價吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只好四處漂泊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡  其實我挺喜歡這種生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我一步都不能踏出這座山還真是令人羡慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣這山就是我的埋骨之地了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我這就去村裡把消息告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我回來之前  不要亂動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你也要在解禁之後再進山裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你也要保重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  保重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無直大師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在也還是無直大師的弟子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從村裡到這裡就是一種鍛煉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在已經是很出色的蟲師了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  他回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉和他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無直大師沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音越來越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是順風的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀古先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那聲音很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近又沒有鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親他們說什麼都沒有聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為蟲的原因嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問你個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經在學「山神」的法術了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「山神」？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使人成為「山神」的法術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,術者在體內飼養「葎」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時常保持駕驅「葎」的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使睡覺的時候  也能感知山上發生的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能操控「葎」的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能掌握抑止這山中異常的精氣的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有開始學習
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  鐘聲的原因並非什麼特別讓人擔心的蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家睡覺去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是去散步而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山又變得寂靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它已經到這裡來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招來不得了的傢伙了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音是從那邊傳來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山頂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  還有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腳根本沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是在那個一般人不會去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚「白蛇」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越近的鐘聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是白蛇的叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專吃靈獸的蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山的靈獸  沼澤的靈獸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了它們之後取而代之
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說  是能給這裡帶來安定的蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做也是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要阻礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡曾有一隻很不錯的靈獸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一隻有著巨大野豬外表的美麗靈獸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了不該做的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話以後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快從這山裡出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經太遲了  白蛇已經找到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該由它來取代靈獸的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對普通人來說太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對小玉我也只是教給他一些生存的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你身上的「葎」剝離
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白費力氣  即使這樣也沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣總比什麼都不做強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裡的人要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可是十分崇拜  十分需要你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過你有些羡慕我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也有些羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  不要隨便就決定去死！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:16:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會被捲進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無直大師？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無直大師——！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  無直來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無直
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  各位  大山怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  今年也發生了幾件奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  無直
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能住下來？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這村子需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有吸引蟲的體質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一個地方住下來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡就變成蟲的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論無何都不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹朔可是一直等著你來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能在這裡和她一起生活嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一定要我住下來的話我有個不情之請
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須得殺死這山上的靈獸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我吃它的肉  之後代替執行它的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話以我的意識就能讓蟲無法接近大山
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也想住下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這種事也必然是無法原諒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈獸必經之地的地圖和毒藥都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔  你去哪裡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  牡丹姐給了我這些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下  我這就拿去下鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力做的好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔…朔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.69,0:19:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一定要住在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這絕不是我的記憶  我在做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到山頂的時候發現銀古先生倒在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到處都找不到無直大師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然之後又仔細找了找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連原來的寺廟也不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且村裡的人誰也記不起無直大師的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被白蛇吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈獸的交替就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而只有那時在山裡的人的記憶還保留著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這種召喚蟲的藥是你調配的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你還蠻厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這些我當然會做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是無直大師的弟子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一棵樹怎麼也砍不倒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能想個好辦法？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵  好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣總比什麼都不做強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然壯觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你是不會知道人們的心情的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  白蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.59,0:22:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是打哈欠一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.46,0:22:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蛇叫了一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.70,0:22:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後靜靜地陷入沉睡之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}眇之魚


